        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Already registered with the Texas Ethics Commission? Your profile is waiting.
          Claim it in 60 seconds and start attracting clients today.
        </p>

